sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Edge Device
    participant E as Edge Management System
    participant O as System Operator
    participant A as Application Publisher
    participant C as Application Certifier<br/>(Optional)

    Note over O,D: Application activation
    O->>E: Activate application
    E->>D: Activate application
    D->>D: Launch application
    D->>D: Record application logs
    D-->>E: Report application status
